FBIS3-4516 "drchi062_a_94009" FBIS-CHI-94-062 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing Mongolian Foreign Minister To Visit 6-11 Apr OW3103084094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0821 GMT 31 Mar 94 OW3103084094 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 31 (XINHUA) -- Tserenpiliyn Gombosuren, minister of external relations of the State of Mongolia, will pay an official visit to China from April 6 to 11 at the invitation of Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen. A Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman made the announcement here today.
